1	in sweet forgetfulness all pain and woe 
1	all in one moment and so near the brink 
1	but fate withstands and to oppose th attempt 
1	medusa with gorgonian terror guards
1	the ford and of itself the water flies
1	all taste of living wight as once it fled
1	the lip of tantalus thus roving on
