1	they passed and many a region dolorous 
1	o er many a frozen many a fiery alp 
1	rocks caves lakes fens bogs dens and shades of death 
1	a universe of death which god by curse
1	created evil for evil only good 
1	where all life dies death lives and nature breeds 
1	perverse all monstrous all prodigious things 
1	obominable inutterable and worse
1	than fables yet have feigned or fear conceived 
1	gorgons and hydras and chimeras dire 
