1	before their eyes in sudden view appear
1	the secrets of the hoary deep a dark
1	illimitable ocean without bound 
1	without dimension where length breadth and height 
1	and time and place are lost where eldest night
1	and chaos ancestors of nature hold
1	eternal anarchy amidst the noise
1	of endless wars and by confusion stand 
1	for hot cold moist and dry four champions fierce 
1	strive here for mastery and to battle bring
1	their embryon atoms they around the flag
1	of each his faction in their several clans 
1	light armed or heavy sharp smooth swift or slow 
1	swarm populous unnumbered as the sands
1	of barca or cyrene s torrid soil 
