1	and flowering odours cassia nard and balm 
1	a wilderness of sweets for nature here
1	wantoned as in her prime and played at will
1	her virgin fancies pouring forth more sweet 
1	wild above rule or art enormous bliss 
1	him through the spicy forest onward come
1	adam discerned as in the door he sat
1	of his cool bower while now the mounted sun
1	shot down direct his fervid rays to warm
1	earth s inmost womb more warmth than adam needs 
