1	comes this way moving seems another morn
1	risen on mid noon some great behest from heaven
1	to us perhaps he brings and will vouchsafe
1	this day to be our guest but go with speed 
1	and what thy stores contain bring forth and pour
1	abundance fit to honour and receive
1	our heavenly stranger well we may afford
