1	among the faithless faithful only he 
1	among innumerable false unmoved 
1	unshaken unseduced unterrified 
1	his loyalty he kept his love his zeal 
1	nor number nor example with him wrought
1	to swerve from truth or change his constant mind 
1	though single from amidst them forth he passed 
1	long way through hostile scorn which he sustained
1	superiour nor of violence feared aught 
1	and with retorted scorn his back he turned
1	on those proud towers to swift destruction doomed 
1	all night the dreadless angel unpursued 
