1	what inward thence i feel not therefore foiled 
1	who meet with various objects from the sense
1	variously representing yet still free 
1	approve the best and follow what i approve 
1	to love thou blamest me not for love thou sayest 
1	leads up to heaven is both the way and guide 
1	bear with me then if lawful what i ask 
