1	doubt might beget of diabolick power
1	active within beyond the sense of brute 
1	thus he resolved but first from inward grief
1	his bursting passion into plaints thus poured 
1	more justly seat worthier of gods as built
1	with second thoughts reforming what was old 
1	o earth how like to heaven if not preferred
1	for what god after better worse would build 
