1	by what i seek but others to make such
1	as i though thereby worse to me redound 
1	for only in destroying i find ease
1	to my relentless thoughts and him destroyed 
1	or won to what may work his utter loss 
1	for whom all this was made all this will soon
1	follow as to him linked in weal or woe 
1	in woe then that destruction wide may range 
1	to me shall be the glory sole among
