1	little inferiour by my adventure hard
1	with peril great achieved long were to tell
1	what i have done what suffered with what pain
1	voyaged th unreal vast unbounded deep
1	of horrible confusion over which
1	by sin and death a broad way now is paved 
1	to expedite your glorious march but i
1	toiled out my uncouth passage forced to ride
