1	as sorted best with present things the sun
1	had first his precept so to move so shine 
1	as might affect the earth with cold and heat
1	scarce tolerable and from the north to call
1	decrepit winter from the south to bring
1	solstitial summer s heat to the blanc moon
1	her office they prescribed to the other five
1	their planetary motions and aspects 
1	in sextile square and trine and opposite 
1	of noxious efficacy and when to join
